<td class="mbox-text" style="">Look up <i><b><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/cevere" class="extiw" title="wiktionary:cevere">cevere</a></b></i> in<br />
<a href="/wiki/Wiktionary" title="Wiktionary">Wiktionary</a>, the free dictionary.</td>
</tr>
